WEBVTT

00:00:06.112 --> 00:00:07.114
[rock music]

00:00:07.114 --> 00:00:14.195
♪ ♪

00:00:21.342 --> 00:00:22.344
[woman singing in Japanese]

00:00:22.344 --> 00:00:29.492
♪ ♪

00:01:39.365 --> 00:01:41.235
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THIS IS THE TALE

00:01:41.235 --> 00:01:42.505
OF A MAN WHO HAS YET TO REALIZE

00:01:42.505 --> 00:01:44.408
WHAT DESTINY HOLDS IN STORE

00:01:44.408 --> 00:01:45.277
FOR HIM.

00:01:45.277 --> 00:01:47.214
SIMON’S LAGANN AND KAMINA’S

00:01:47.214 --> 00:01:48.851
GURREN PERFECT THEIR COMBINATION

00:01:48.851 --> 00:01:50.187
TECHNIQUE...

00:01:50.187 --> 00:01:51.824
AND THE RESULT IS NAMED

00:01:51.824 --> 00:01:53.259
GURREN LAGANN.

00:01:53.259 --> 00:01:54.529
THEIR JOURNEY IN SEARCH

00:01:54.529 --> 00:01:56.199
OF THE ENEMY’S HEADQUARTERS

00:01:56.199 --> 00:01:57.134
CONTINUES.

00:01:57.134 --> 00:01:59.573
HOWEVER...

00:02:01.744 --> 00:02:02.746
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU KNOW, WE HAVEN’T

00:02:02.746 --> 00:02:04.215
SEEN ANY GUNMEN LATELY.

00:02:04.215 --> 00:02:05.585
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU HAVE A POINT.

00:02:05.585 --> 00:02:06.352
I DON’T WANT MY SKILLS TO

00:02:06.352 --> 00:02:07.388
GET RUSTY.

00:02:07.388 --> 00:02:08.724
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU DOING HERE

00:02:08.724 --> 00:02:09.826
IN MY GUNMEN, ANYWAY?

00:02:09.826 --> 00:02:11.664
DIDN’T WE BUILD YOU A TRANSPORT

00:02:11.664 --> 00:02:12.666
OUT OF WRECKAGE AND SCRAPS?

00:02:12.666 --> 00:02:13.768
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YEAH, YOU DID, BUT THIS

00:02:13.768 --> 00:02:14.770
IS THE BEST PLACE TO BE WHEN

00:02:14.770 --> 00:02:15.838
WE’RE MOVING.

00:02:15.838 --> 00:02:17.174
THAT THING BOUNCES AROUND

00:02:17.174 --> 00:02:17.542
TOO MUCH.

00:02:17.542 --> 00:02:18.577
IT’S MURDER ON MY BUTT.

00:02:18.577 --> 00:02:19.546
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU SURE IT’S NOT

00:02:19.546 --> 00:02:22.384
’CAUSE YOUR ASS IS TOO BIG?

00:02:22.384 --> 00:02:23.654
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT D’YA SAY?!

00:02:23.654 --> 00:02:25.424
YEAH, NOW THIS IS COMFY!

00:02:25.424 --> 00:02:26.593
&gt;&gt; Kamina: JEEZ, YOKO,

00:02:26.593 --> 00:02:27.862
YOU’RE HEAVY!

00:02:27.862 --> 00:02:28.698
IT’S LIKE YOUR BRAINS HAVE

00:02:28.698 --> 00:02:29.766
DROPPED DOWN OUTTA YOUR SKULL

00:02:29.766 --> 00:02:30.635
AND SETTLED INTO YOUR ASS, YOU

00:02:30.635 --> 00:02:31.603
IDIOT CHICK.

00:02:31.603 --> 00:02:32.739
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OH, YOU THINK SO,

00:02:32.739 --> 00:02:33.541
DO YA?

00:02:33.541 --> 00:02:34.543
SOUNDS TO ME LIKE YOU’RE HUNGRY.

00:02:34.543 --> 00:02:36.580
WANNA TASTE MY MEATBALL BULLETS?

00:02:36.580 --> 00:02:38.483
&gt;&gt; Kamina: NO, NOT THOSE!

00:02:38.483 --> 00:02:41.724
&gt;&gt; Ron: HMM.

00:02:41.724 --> 00:02:43.326
THE SURFACE AROUND HERE SEEMS

00:02:43.326 --> 00:02:44.730
TO HAVE FORMED COMPARATIVELY

00:02:44.730 --> 00:02:45.430
RECENTLY.

00:02:45.430 --> 00:02:46.800
&gt;&gt; Simon: HOW RECENTLY?

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.571
&gt;&gt; Ron: OH, I’D SAY, UH,

00:02:48.571 --> 00:02:49.606
SOMEWHERE AROUND FOUR OR FIVE

00:02:49.606 --> 00:02:51.510
HUNDRED YEARS AGO, MAYBE.

00:02:51.510 --> 00:02:52.612
&gt;&gt; Kamina: OW! DON’T SHOOT,

00:02:52.612 --> 00:02:53.413
YOU CRAZY BITCH!

00:02:53.413 --> 00:02:54.315
YOU’LL KILL ME!

00:02:54.315 --> 00:02:54.883
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THESE LITTLE THINGS

00:02:54.883 --> 00:02:56.787
WON’T KILL YOU, YOU BIG BABY!

00:02:56.787 --> 00:02:58.390
&gt;&gt; Ron: BE CAREFUL!

00:02:58.390 --> 00:03:00.928
&gt;&gt; Simon: HEY, WATCH IT!

00:03:00.928 --> 00:03:01.764
&gt;&gt; Ron: THEY NEVER GET TIRED OF

00:03:01.764 --> 00:03:04.168
FIGHTING, DO THEY?

00:03:04.168 --> 00:03:11.215
[Kamina and Yoko screaming]

00:03:11.215 --> 00:03:12.418
&gt;&gt; Simon: THEY JUST FELL THROUGH

00:03:12.418 --> 00:03:12.919
THE GROUND.

00:03:12.919 --> 00:03:19.365
[rocks cracking]

00:03:19.365 --> 00:03:19.699
[Simon yells]

00:03:19.699 --> 00:03:20.935
&gt;&gt; Ron: MY, WHAT AN

00:03:20.935 --> 00:03:21.637
ENORMOUS CAVERN!

00:03:21.637 --> 00:03:22.471
I’VE NEVER SEEN ANYTHING LIKE

00:03:22.471 --> 00:03:23.641
IT‐‐IT’S‐‐

00:03:23.641 --> 00:03:24.776
&gt;&gt; Simon: HOW FAR DOWN DOES THIS

00:03:24.776 --> 00:03:26.847
THING GO‐O‐O‐O?!

00:03:26.847 --> 00:03:30.855
[yelling]

00:03:45.283 --> 00:03:49.893
[amazed chatter]

00:03:55.671 --> 00:03:56.874
[gasps]

00:03:56.874 --> 00:03:59.679
[whimpering]

00:03:59.679 --> 00:04:03.319
[people gasp]

00:04:03.319 --> 00:04:06.927
[water splashes]

00:04:06.927 --> 00:04:07.862
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WELL, I GUESS IT’S

00:04:07.862 --> 00:04:08.764
A GOOD THING I CAME

00:04:08.764 --> 00:04:11.603
AROUND FIRST.

00:04:11.603 --> 00:04:12.772
&gt;&gt; PEOPLE HAVE COME TO US FROM

00:04:12.772 --> 00:04:13.607
THE FACE GOD!

00:04:13.607 --> 00:04:14.643
&gt;&gt; MESSENGERS FROM THE

00:04:14.643 --> 00:04:15.812
CELESTIAL LANDS!

00:04:15.812 --> 00:04:16.647
&gt;&gt; Kamina: DID THAT GUY JUST

00:04:16.647 --> 00:04:19.886
SAY, "FACE GOD"?

00:04:19.886 --> 00:04:22.324
THAT’S A...

00:04:22.324 --> 00:04:25.965
THAT’S A GUNMEN!

00:04:25.965 --> 00:04:26.733
WHAT A WRECK.

00:04:26.733 --> 00:04:27.535
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: PLEASE DON’T

00:04:27.535 --> 00:04:31.844
TOUCH THAT!

00:04:31.844 --> 00:04:32.846
DON’T TOUCH IT.

00:04:32.846 --> 00:04:35.685
IT IS OUR GUARDIAN DEITY.

00:04:35.685 --> 00:04:38.824
[sneeze]

00:04:38.824 --> 00:04:40.661
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YO, FOREHEAD BOY!

00:04:40.661 --> 00:04:41.563
DON’T YOU HAVE ANYTHING ELSE WE

00:04:41.563 --> 00:04:42.297
CAN THROW ON THE FIRE?

00:04:42.297 --> 00:04:43.634
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: MY NAME IS ROSSIU.

00:04:43.634 --> 00:04:44.803
AND I’M AFRAID THAT WHAT WE’VE

00:04:44.803 --> 00:04:46.405
GIVEN YOU IS ALL WE HAVE.

00:04:46.405 --> 00:04:47.675
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THIS PLACE IS A

00:04:47.675 --> 00:04:48.744
BARREL OF LAUGHS, AIN’T IT?

00:04:48.744 --> 00:04:50.882
&gt;&gt; Yoko: HEY! DON’T BE RUDE!

00:04:50.882 --> 00:04:52.919
&gt;&gt; SO DID YOU GUYS REALLY COME

00:04:52.919 --> 00:04:54.923
FROM THE CELESTIAL LANDS?

00:04:54.923 --> 00:04:55.892
&gt;&gt; ARE YOU MESSENGERS FROM THE

00:04:55.892 --> 00:04:57.060
FACE GOD OR SOMETHING?

00:04:57.060 --> 00:04:57.962
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, FOREHEAD, WHAT’S

00:04:57.962 --> 00:04:58.964
THE DEAL WITH THESE KIDS?

00:04:58.964 --> 00:04:59.933
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: GIMMY, DARRY, STOP

00:04:59.933 --> 00:05:01.670
BOTHERING OUR GUESTS.

00:05:01.670 --> 00:05:02.806
GO SOMEWHERE ELSE.

00:05:02.806 --> 00:05:04.910
&gt;&gt; OKAY!

00:05:04.910 --> 00:05:06.647
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I’M VERY SORRY.

00:05:06.647 --> 00:05:07.515
I’M AFRAID THAT THESE TWO

00:05:07.515 --> 00:05:08.918
CHILDREN HAVE NO PARENTS.

00:05:08.918 --> 00:05:09.853
EVERYONE SPOILS THEM ’CAUSE

00:05:09.853 --> 00:05:10.387
OF THAT.

00:05:10.387 --> 00:05:10.822
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHATEVER.

00:05:10.822 --> 00:05:12.291
WHO CARES ABOUT THAT?

00:05:12.291 --> 00:05:13.493
ALL I CARE ABOUT IS WHAT THAT

00:05:13.493 --> 00:05:14.629
GUNMEN’S DOING THERE.

00:05:14.629 --> 00:05:15.430
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: GUNMEN?

00:05:15.430 --> 00:05:16.967
YOU REFER TO THE FACE GOD?

00:05:16.967 --> 00:05:17.969
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WAIT, YOU DON’T KNOW

00:05:17.969 --> 00:05:18.838
WHAT THAT IS?

00:05:18.838 --> 00:05:19.606
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU WEREN’T ANY

00:05:19.606 --> 00:05:21.075
DIFFERENT NOT TOO LONG AGO.

00:05:21.075 --> 00:05:22.679
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHAT THE HELL?!

00:05:22.679 --> 00:05:23.581
WHAT’D I DO TO DESERVE ALL THIS

00:05:23.581 --> 00:05:25.050
GRIEF FROM YOU?

00:05:25.050 --> 00:05:27.722
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OH, SHUT UP!

00:05:27.722 --> 00:05:28.757
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: EXCUSE ME.

00:05:28.757 --> 00:05:29.826
MISS YOKO, IS IT?

00:05:29.826 --> 00:05:31.630
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YEAH?

00:05:31.630 --> 00:05:32.932
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: SORRY ABOUT THIS,

00:05:32.932 --> 00:05:34.401
BUT WOULD YOU MIND PUTTING

00:05:34.401 --> 00:05:35.805
THIS ROBE ON?

00:05:35.805 --> 00:05:36.607
&gt;&gt; Yoko: SURE.

00:05:36.607 --> 00:05:37.040
WHAT FOR?

00:05:37.040 --> 00:05:38.811
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WELL, UM, THE THING

00:05:38.811 --> 00:05:40.882
IS, I NEED FOR YOU TO COVER UP.

00:05:40.882 --> 00:05:42.484
YOUR MANNER OF DRESS, IT’S‐‐

00:05:42.484 --> 00:05:43.821
WELL, IT’S‐‐IT’S INDECENT!

00:05:43.821 --> 00:05:45.758
[surprised exclamation]

00:05:45.758 --> 00:05:49.933
[Boota grunts quizzically]

00:05:49.933 --> 00:05:51.102
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I’M NOT TOO CRAZY ABOUT

00:05:51.102 --> 00:05:52.004
THESE CLOTHES.

00:05:52.004 --> 00:05:53.439
THEY’RE TOO RESTRICTING.

00:05:53.439 --> 00:05:54.341
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HMM...

00:05:54.341 --> 00:05:56.613
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT IS IT NOW?

00:05:56.613 --> 00:05:57.481
&gt;&gt; Kamina: BOY, TAKE AWAY THE

00:05:57.481 --> 00:05:58.984
BARE MIDRIFF AND YOU DON’T HAVE

00:05:58.984 --> 00:06:00.788
ANYTHING LEFT, DO YA?

00:06:00.788 --> 00:06:03.493
[Boota grunts excitedly]

00:06:03.493 --> 00:06:08.436
[Simon gasps]

00:06:08.436 --> 00:06:09.940
[Kamina groans]

00:06:09.940 --> 00:06:11.810
&gt;&gt; Yoko: DIRT‐BALL SCUMBAG!

00:06:11.810 --> 00:06:12.946
ROTTEN STINKING LOUSE!

00:06:12.946 --> 00:06:14.448
YOU ARE ONE HOPELESS PERVERT

00:06:14.448 --> 00:06:16.352
OF A MAN, YOU KNOW THAT?

00:06:16.352 --> 00:06:17.956
DON’T PICK UP HIS BAD HABITS,

00:06:17.956 --> 00:06:18.824
SIMON!

00:06:18.824 --> 00:06:19.759
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: PLEASE CEASE

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:20.928
THIS BEHAVIOR!

00:06:20.928 --> 00:06:21.897
I WOULD EXPECT CELESTIANS

00:06:21.897 --> 00:06:23.032
TO REFRAIN FROM SUCH LEWD

00:06:23.032 --> 00:06:24.569
CONDUCT IN THE PRESENCE

00:06:24.569 --> 00:06:25.972
OF OUR VILLAGERS.

00:06:25.972 --> 00:06:27.775
&gt;&gt; DID YOU SAY, "CELESTIANS"?

00:06:27.775 --> 00:06:29.813
ARE YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

00:06:29.813 --> 00:06:30.982
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YES. THEY ARE

00:06:30.982 --> 00:06:32.518
CELESTIANS, FOR THEY HAVE COME

00:06:32.518 --> 00:06:33.554
TO US IN THE COMPANY OF

00:06:33.554 --> 00:06:33.954
FACE GODS.

00:06:33.954 --> 00:06:35.056
WE SHOULD SHOW THEM THE RESPECT

00:06:35.056 --> 00:06:35.958
THEY’RE DUE.

00:06:35.958 --> 00:06:36.994
&gt;&gt; ROSSIU!

00:06:36.994 --> 00:06:37.895
[labored breathing]

00:06:37.895 --> 00:06:38.998
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WHAT’S THE MATTER?

00:06:38.998 --> 00:06:40.801
&gt;&gt; THERE’S A PROBLEM.

00:06:40.801 --> 00:06:41.837
IT’S UCOM’S WIFE.

00:06:41.837 --> 00:06:43.139
SHE JUST GAVE BIRTH.

00:06:43.139 --> 00:06:44.643
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: BUT THIS IS

00:06:44.643 --> 00:06:45.578
GOOD NEWS!

00:06:45.578 --> 00:06:47.014
ACTUALLY, I WAS ABOUT

00:06:47.014 --> 00:06:47.982
TO SUGGEST TO OUR GUESTS THAT

00:06:47.982 --> 00:06:49.385
WE GO VISIT THE HIGH PRIEST.

00:06:49.385 --> 00:06:51.022
&gt;&gt; THE PROBLEM IS THAT SHE NOT

00:06:51.022 --> 00:06:52.859
ONLY HAD A NEWBORN GIRL, BUT SHE

00:06:52.859 --> 00:06:54.863
ALSO HAD A PAIR OF BOYS!

00:06:54.863 --> 00:06:55.564
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WHAT DID YOU

00:06:55.564 --> 00:06:55.965
JUST SAY?!

00:06:55.965 --> 00:06:57.702
&gt;&gt; DID YOU HEAR THAT?

00:06:57.702 --> 00:07:00.875
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HUH? WHAT’S THE DEAL?

00:07:00.875 --> 00:07:02.879
&gt;&gt; TRIPLETS, YOU SAY?

00:07:02.879 --> 00:07:04.081
BORN TO UCOM’S WIFE?

00:07:04.081 --> 00:07:05.450
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YES.

00:07:05.450 --> 00:07:06.787
&gt;&gt; THAT BRINGS THE VILLAGE’S

00:07:06.787 --> 00:07:08.991
POPULATION TO 52.

00:07:08.991 --> 00:07:10.193
WE HAVE NO CHOICE THEN.

00:07:10.193 --> 00:07:11.863
WE MUST CHOOSE TWO.

00:07:11.863 --> 00:07:13.066
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: FATHER MAGIN, MUST WE

00:07:13.066 --> 00:07:13.968
REALLY MAKE OUR PEOPLE

00:07:13.968 --> 00:07:17.040
GO THROUGH WITH THIS?

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:18.476
&gt;&gt; Magin: ROSSIU, DO YOU NOT

00:07:18.476 --> 00:07:19.478
UNDERSTAND?

00:07:19.478 --> 00:07:20.648
THIS RITE BESTOWS A

00:07:20.648 --> 00:07:22.017
GREAT BLESSING.

00:07:22.017 --> 00:07:24.021
WE WILL CELEBRATE THE CHOSEN,

00:07:24.021 --> 00:07:28.831
JUST AS WE DID WITH YOUR MOTHER.

00:07:28.831 --> 00:07:29.766
&gt;&gt; Kamina: MAN, THIS PLACE

00:07:29.766 --> 00:07:31.035
IS DEPRESSING.

00:07:31.035 --> 00:07:32.739
OLD GIHA VILLAGE WAS NOTHING

00:07:32.739 --> 00:07:34.174
LIKE THIS GLOOMFEST.

00:07:34.174 --> 00:07:35.945
SO IS IT TIME TO EAT YET

00:07:35.945 --> 00:07:36.880
OR WHAT?

00:07:36.880 --> 00:07:37.882
&gt;&gt; Simon: UH, I THINK THIS

00:07:37.882 --> 00:07:38.449
WAS IT.

00:07:38.449 --> 00:07:39.051
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THIS AIN’T ENOUGH

00:07:39.051 --> 00:07:39.686
FOOD FOR ME!

00:07:39.686 --> 00:07:41.489
I NEED ME SOME MEAT, MY FRIEND,

00:07:41.489 --> 00:07:43.627
SOME TASTY, DELICIOUS MEAT!

00:07:43.627 --> 00:07:44.963
[Boota squeaks]

00:07:44.963 --> 00:07:45.965
&gt;&gt; Ron: YOU KNOW, I THINK THIS

00:07:45.965 --> 00:07:47.869
MAY BE A GRAND WELCOME FOR US.

00:07:47.869 --> 00:07:48.704
THESE PEOPLE HAVE NO

00:07:48.704 --> 00:07:50.574
ELECTRICITY, NO LIVESTOCK.

00:07:50.574 --> 00:07:51.777
ALL THEY HAVE HERE IS A TINY

00:07:51.777 --> 00:07:54.181
POND AND A BROKEN GUNMEN.

00:07:54.181 --> 00:07:54.983
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I BET EVEN A MEASLY

00:07:54.983 --> 00:07:56.653
MEAL LIKE THIS IS PRECIOUS TO

00:07:56.653 --> 00:07:57.120
THEM.

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:58.724
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: MY APOLOGIES.

00:07:58.724 --> 00:07:59.191
IT SOUNDS LIKE THE MEAL

00:07:59.191 --> 00:08:00.661
WAS NOT TO YOUR LIKING.

00:08:00.661 --> 00:08:04.468
[gasps nervously]

00:08:04.468 --> 00:08:05.871
I WAS HOPING, IF IT’S NOT

00:08:05.871 --> 00:08:07.074
TOO MUCH TROUBLE, I WAS HOPING

00:08:07.074 --> 00:08:08.109
I MIGHT IMPOSE ON YOU

00:08:08.109 --> 00:08:09.078
TO TELL ME A LITTLE BIT

00:08:09.078 --> 00:08:10.113
ABOUT THE CELESTIAL LANDS?

00:08:10.113 --> 00:08:11.248
&gt;&gt; Kamina: LOOK AT YOU,

00:08:11.248 --> 00:08:11.950
FOREHEAD BOY.

00:08:11.950 --> 00:08:12.919
DOES THIS MEAN THAT YOU’RE

00:08:12.919 --> 00:08:13.787
WANTING MORE THAN THE LIFE

00:08:13.787 --> 00:08:15.056
OF A CELLAR DWELLER?

00:08:15.056 --> 00:08:16.593
FIRST, ALLOW ME TO GET THIS OUT

00:08:16.593 --> 00:08:17.729
OF THE WAY!

00:08:17.729 --> 00:08:18.731
I HATE TO BREAK IT TO YOU, KID,

00:08:18.731 --> 00:08:19.866
BUT GUNMEN ARE NOT GODS!

00:08:19.866 --> 00:08:21.135
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: BUT THAT HAS BEEN OUR

00:08:21.135 --> 00:08:21.970
BELIEF SINCE LONG BEFORE I WAS

00:08:21.970 --> 00:08:22.939
BORN.

00:08:22.939 --> 00:08:23.941
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOUR PEOPLE HAVE

00:08:23.941 --> 00:08:25.010
ALWAYS LIVED LIKE THIS?

00:08:25.010 --> 00:08:26.780
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: NO. THEY SAY THAT OUR

00:08:26.780 --> 00:08:28.116
LOT HAS IMPROVED CONSIDERABLY

00:08:28.116 --> 00:08:29.652
SINCE THE HIGH PRIEST TOOK OVER

00:08:29.652 --> 00:08:30.621
THE ADMINISTRATION OF THE

00:08:30.621 --> 00:08:31.122
VILLAGE.

00:08:31.122 --> 00:08:33.059
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THIS HIGH PRIEST GUY.

00:08:33.059 --> 00:08:33.994
WHO IS HE?

00:08:33.994 --> 00:08:36.265
&gt;&gt; PARDON ME, CELESTIANS.

00:08:36.265 --> 00:08:38.202
PLEASE DO NOT TEST THIS BOY’S

00:08:38.202 --> 00:08:40.073
PIETY ANY FURTHER.

00:08:40.073 --> 00:08:40.908
SAY NO MORE OF WHERE YOU COME

00:08:40.908 --> 00:08:41.843
FROM.

00:08:41.843 --> 00:08:43.146
YOUR WORDS ARE TOO MUCH FOR OUR

00:08:43.146 --> 00:08:44.949
PEOPLE.

00:08:44.949 --> 00:08:45.718
&gt;&gt; Ron: SO ARE YOU THE HIGH

00:08:45.718 --> 00:08:46.753
PRIEST THEN?

00:08:46.753 --> 00:08:47.989
&gt;&gt; I APOLOGIZE FOR NOT

00:08:47.989 --> 00:08:49.626
INTRODUCING MYSELF.

00:08:49.626 --> 00:08:51.797
I AM MAGIN, AND IT IS MY DUTY

00:08:51.797 --> 00:08:52.999
TO GOVERN THIS VILLAGE.

00:08:52.999 --> 00:08:54.034
&gt;&gt; Kamina: IS THAT A FACT?

00:08:54.034 --> 00:08:55.538
YOU’RE THE HEAD HONCHO OF THIS

00:08:55.538 --> 00:08:58.877
SORRY LITTLE DUMP?

00:08:58.877 --> 00:09:00.748
&gt;&gt; ROSSIU, WE HAVE AN IMPORTANT

00:09:00.748 --> 00:09:02.117
CEREMONY TOMORROW.

00:09:02.117 --> 00:09:02.919
PLEASE GO TO BED.

00:09:02.919 --> 00:09:04.021
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YES, FATHER.

00:09:04.021 --> 00:09:05.256
&gt;&gt; YOU AND YOUR COMPANIONS

00:09:05.256 --> 00:09:06.526
SHOULD TURN IN FOR THE EVENING

00:09:06.526 --> 00:09:07.160
AS WELL.

00:09:07.160 --> 00:09:09.833
IF YOU’LL EXCUSE ME.

00:09:09.833 --> 00:09:10.634
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHAT’S WITH YOU?

00:09:10.634 --> 00:09:11.268
&gt;&gt; Yoko: ARE YOU AN EVEN BIGGER

00:09:11.268 --> 00:09:12.939
MORON THAN I THOUGHT YOU WERE?

00:09:12.939 --> 00:09:13.707
WHY ARE YOU ACTING...

00:09:13.707 --> 00:09:14.542
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I DON’T LIKE

00:09:14.542 --> 00:09:15.176
THAT GUY.

00:09:15.176 --> 00:09:16.646
NOT HIS UGLY MUG OR

00:09:16.646 --> 00:09:17.715
HIS ATTITUDE.

00:09:17.715 --> 00:09:19.853
&gt;&gt; Yoko: HEY!

00:09:31.910 --> 00:09:39.692
♪ ♪

00:10:00.668 --> 00:10:02.037
[gears turn]

00:10:02.037 --> 00:10:06.145
[rumbling]

00:10:15.296 --> 00:10:16.198
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WOW!

00:10:16.198 --> 00:10:17.367
THE THING STILL WORKS!

00:10:17.367 --> 00:10:19.238
&gt;&gt; Simon: G‐GOOD MORNING.

00:10:19.238 --> 00:10:20.240
&gt;&gt; Kamina: TAKE IT FOR A SPIN,

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:21.175
FOREHEAD BOY.

00:10:21.175 --> 00:10:22.144
THE ONLY KEY YOU NEED TO GET

00:10:22.144 --> 00:10:23.714
THAT THING GOING IS A FIGHTING

00:10:23.714 --> 00:10:24.916
SPIRIT!

00:10:24.916 --> 00:10:26.352
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I‐I HAD NO INTENTION

00:10:26.352 --> 00:10:27.788
OF DOING ANYTHING...

00:10:27.788 --> 00:10:28.289
&gt;&gt; Kamina: COME ON!

00:10:28.289 --> 00:10:29.258
RELAX AND PUT EVERYTHING ELSE

00:10:29.258 --> 00:10:30.728
OUT OF YOUR MIND!

00:10:30.728 --> 00:10:31.863
GO AHEAD, FOREHEAD BOY!

00:10:31.863 --> 00:10:33.199
DO WHATEVER FEELS NATURAL!

00:10:33.199 --> 00:10:36.105
IT’S A GREAT FEELING.

00:10:36.105 --> 00:10:37.942
&gt;&gt; ROSSIU!

00:10:37.942 --> 00:10:39.779
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: F‐FATHER MAGIN!

00:10:39.779 --> 00:10:41.215
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THERE HE IS AGAIN.

00:10:41.215 --> 00:10:42.017
&gt;&gt; WHAT DO YOU THINK YOU’RE

00:10:42.017 --> 00:10:43.787
DOING, ROSSIU?

00:10:43.787 --> 00:10:45.624
WHO TOLD YOU YOU COULD TOUCH

00:10:45.624 --> 00:10:47.093
THE FACE GOD?

00:10:47.093 --> 00:10:49.064
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I‐I APOLOGIZE.

00:10:49.064 --> 00:10:49.999
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HEY, HANG ON

00:10:49.999 --> 00:10:51.302
A MINUTE, OLD‐TIMER!

00:10:51.302 --> 00:10:52.939
JUST NOW, IT FINALLY CAME TO ME.

00:10:52.939 --> 00:10:53.941
&gt;&gt; Simon: BRO, WHAT’RE YOU

00:10:53.941 --> 00:10:54.374
DOING?

00:10:54.374 --> 00:10:55.945
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I’VE BEEN TRYIN’ TO

00:10:55.945 --> 00:10:56.880
FIGURE OUT WHY YOUR UGLY MUG

00:10:56.880 --> 00:10:58.249
PISSES ME OFF SO MUCH, AND I

00:10:58.249 --> 00:10:59.251
REALIZED YOU LOOK LIKE OUR OLD

00:10:59.251 --> 00:11:00.253
VILLAGE CHIEF.

00:11:00.253 --> 00:11:01.790
RIGHT, SIMON?

00:11:01.790 --> 00:11:03.359
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOU REALLY THINK SO?

00:11:03.359 --> 00:11:04.394
&gt;&gt; YOU AND YOUR FRIENDS...

00:11:04.394 --> 00:11:05.296
&gt;&gt; Kamina: OH, YOU WANNA FIGHT,

00:11:05.296 --> 00:11:06.365
DO YOU?!

00:11:06.365 --> 00:11:07.935
&gt;&gt; YOU OUGHT TO LEAVE OUR

00:11:07.935 --> 00:11:09.304
VILLAGE, AS I BELIEVE YOU HAVE

00:11:09.304 --> 00:11:10.206
NO MORE BUSINESS HERE.

00:11:10.206 --> 00:11:13.246
&gt;&gt; Kamina: SAY WHAT?!

00:11:21.730 --> 00:11:23.232
&gt;&gt; FATHER MAGIN, SURELY

00:11:23.232 --> 00:11:24.234
THE RITUAL DOESN’T NEED TO BE

00:11:24.234 --> 00:11:24.969
HELD NOW.

00:11:24.969 --> 00:11:26.405
CAN’T WE WAIT A LITTLE WHILE?

00:11:26.405 --> 00:11:27.808
I MEAN, AFTER ALL, PERHAPS ALL

00:11:27.808 --> 00:11:28.877
THREE OF THEM WON’T EVEN SURVIVE

00:11:28.877 --> 00:11:30.213
THE FIRST FEW MONTHS.

00:11:30.213 --> 00:11:32.050
&gt;&gt; PLEASE DO NOT MISUNDERSTAND,

00:11:32.050 --> 00:11:33.219
UCOM.

00:11:33.219 --> 00:11:34.254
THOSE FORTUNATE ENOUGH TO BE

00:11:34.254 --> 00:11:35.991
CHOSEN RECEIVE THE BLESSING OF

00:11:35.991 --> 00:11:37.260
THE GODS.

00:11:37.260 --> 00:11:40.333
NOW YOU MUST DRAW, UCOM.

00:11:40.333 --> 00:11:41.468
&gt;&gt; TH‐‐THEN I’LL DRAW.

00:11:41.468 --> 00:11:43.172
I’LL DRAW FOR ME AND FOR MY WIFE

00:11:43.172 --> 00:11:46.746
AND FOR MY CHILDREN.

00:11:49.919 --> 00:11:51.990
&gt;&gt; NEXT COME FORWARD AND DRAW.

00:11:51.990 --> 00:11:55.731
&gt;&gt; YES, FATHER.

00:12:04.782 --> 00:12:05.383
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IS THERE ANYONE

00:12:05.383 --> 00:12:07.020
REMAINING WHO HAS NOT DRAWN

00:12:07.020 --> 00:12:07.354
A LOT?

00:12:07.354 --> 00:12:09.358
&gt;&gt; GIMMY HASN’T DRAWN A LOT YET.

00:12:09.358 --> 00:12:11.128
&gt;&gt; NEITHER HAS DARRY!

00:12:11.128 --> 00:12:13.232
&gt;&gt; OH, YES, MY APOLOGIES.

00:12:13.232 --> 00:12:14.101
YOU TWO ARE THE LAST ONES

00:12:14.101 --> 00:12:16.773
TO DRAW.

00:12:16.773 --> 00:12:19.278
[giggle]

00:12:19.278 --> 00:12:20.714
NOW, MY FRIENDS, OPEN YOUR

00:12:20.714 --> 00:12:21.315
HANDS.

00:12:21.315 --> 00:12:22.952
IF YOUR LOT HAS A MARK,

00:12:22.952 --> 00:12:23.419
YOU HAVE BEEN CHOSEN

00:12:23.419 --> 00:12:25.323
BY THE GODS.

00:12:25.323 --> 00:12:31.970
[relieved murmurs]

00:12:31.970 --> 00:12:33.239
&gt;&gt; SHE WON!

00:12:33.239 --> 00:12:34.241
HEY! DARRY WON!

00:12:34.241 --> 00:12:35.778
&gt;&gt; HEY, SO DID YOU, GIMMY!

00:12:35.778 --> 00:12:36.278
LOOKIT!

00:12:36.278 --> 00:12:37.414
&gt;&gt; WOW, YOU’RE RIGHT, I DID!

00:12:37.414 --> 00:12:38.482
WE BOTH WON!

00:12:38.482 --> 00:12:39.953
&gt;&gt; WE WON! YEAH!

00:12:39.953 --> 00:12:44.328
&gt;&gt; WE WON, WE WON! WOW!

00:12:47.467 --> 00:12:49.071
&gt;&gt; Kamina: HUH?

00:12:49.071 --> 00:12:50.340
I DON’T UNDERSTAND.

00:12:50.340 --> 00:12:51.308
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

00:12:51.308 --> 00:12:52.878
&gt;&gt; Simon: BRO, WHAT HE’S SAYING

00:12:52.878 --> 00:12:53.513
IS THAT HE WANTS THESE KIDS

00:12:53.513 --> 00:12:54.849
TO COME ALONG WITH US.

00:12:54.849 --> 00:12:56.085
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: TRADITION DICTATES

00:12:56.085 --> 00:12:57.120
THAT WHENEVER OUR POPULATION

00:12:57.120 --> 00:12:58.790
EXCEEDS 50, SOME ARE CHOSEN

00:12:58.790 --> 00:13:00.360
BY THE GODS TO BE THE GODS’

00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:02.230
CHILDREN AND ARE SENT UP

00:13:02.230 --> 00:13:03.265
TO THE CELESTIAL LANDS.

00:13:03.265 --> 00:13:04.836
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THE "CELESTIAL LANDS"?

00:13:04.836 --> 00:13:06.238
YOU MEAN THE SURFACE!

00:13:06.238 --> 00:13:09.277
YOU CAN’T SEND THESE KIDS THERE!

00:13:09.277 --> 00:13:11.315
&gt;&gt; SO THAT IS YOUR ANSWER THEN?

00:13:11.315 --> 00:13:12.484
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU HANDLE REJECTION

00:13:12.484 --> 00:13:13.820
A LOT BETTER THAN I THOUGHT

00:13:13.820 --> 00:13:14.154
YOU WOULD.

00:13:14.154 --> 00:13:15.858
&gt;&gt; Simon: I COULD BE WRONG, BUT,

00:13:15.858 --> 00:13:16.860
UH, I’M PRETTY SURE THAT’S NOT

00:13:16.860 --> 00:13:18.029
WHAT’S HAPPENING.

00:13:18.029 --> 00:13:20.299
&gt;&gt; YOU LEAVE US WITH NO CHOICE.

00:13:20.299 --> 00:13:21.368
IF YOU WILL NOT TAKE THEM,

00:13:21.368 --> 00:13:22.470
THEN WE MUST CONDUCT OUR

00:13:22.470 --> 00:13:24.174
CEREMONY IN THE USUAL MANNER.

00:13:24.174 --> 00:13:24.842
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WAIT JUST

00:13:24.842 --> 00:13:25.343
A DAMN MINUTE!

00:13:25.343 --> 00:13:26.278
WHAT’S ONE OR TWO MORE KIDS

00:13:26.278 --> 00:13:27.280
RUNNING AROUND?

00:13:27.280 --> 00:13:29.217
YOU DON’T HAVE TO KICK ’EM OUT!

00:13:29.217 --> 00:13:30.821
&gt;&gt; TO BE CAST OUT AND SENT UP TO

00:13:30.821 --> 00:13:32.223
THE CELESTIAL LANDS IS TO BE

00:13:32.223 --> 00:13:33.960
RELEASED FROM ALL OF THE SORROWS

00:13:33.960 --> 00:13:35.363
THIS LIFE HOLDS.

00:13:35.363 --> 00:13:36.866
IT IS TO RISE UP AND LIVE WITH

00:13:36.866 --> 00:13:37.500
THE GODS.

00:13:37.500 --> 00:13:39.271
IT IS THE ULTIMATE HAPPINESS.

00:13:39.271 --> 00:13:40.306
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THAT’S CRAZY.

00:13:40.306 --> 00:13:41.810
WHY’S IT GOTTA BE THIS WAY?

00:13:41.810 --> 00:13:42.444
SERIOUSLY, I DON’T GET IT,

00:13:42.444 --> 00:13:43.814
NOT ONE BIT!

00:13:43.814 --> 00:13:44.949
HAS ANYBODY EVER CONSIDERED

00:13:44.949 --> 00:13:46.085
GOING UP THERE TO SEE WHAT IT’S

00:13:46.085 --> 00:13:47.855
REALLY LIKE?

00:13:47.855 --> 00:13:48.957
&gt;&gt; COME ON, MISTER!

00:13:48.957 --> 00:13:50.226
PLEASE TAKE US THERE!

00:13:50.226 --> 00:13:51.261
&gt;&gt; WHAT ARE THE CELESTIAL LANDS

00:13:51.261 --> 00:13:52.097
LIKE?

00:13:52.097 --> 00:13:53.099
&gt;&gt; Kamina: IT AIN’T EXACTLY

00:13:53.099 --> 00:13:54.000
PARADISE UP THERE, I’LL TELL YA

00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:54.869
THAT MUCH!

00:13:54.869 --> 00:13:56.105
NO WAY CAN WE DRAG TWO KIDS

00:13:56.105 --> 00:13:56.539
AROUND!

00:13:56.539 --> 00:13:57.273
&gt;&gt; WHY NOT, MISTER?!

00:13:57.273 --> 00:13:58.009
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE MEAN!

00:13:58.009 --> 00:13:59.044
&gt;&gt; MEANIE!

00:13:59.044 --> 00:14:00.013
&gt;&gt; WOULD YOU PLEASE STOP

00:14:00.013 --> 00:14:02.217
BERATING THE WAYS OF OUR PEOPLE?

00:14:02.217 --> 00:14:03.553
STOP INSULTING OUR CUSTOMS.

00:14:03.553 --> 00:14:04.287
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I’M SORRY.

00:14:04.287 --> 00:14:05.256
EXCUSE ME?

00:14:05.256 --> 00:14:06.860
LOOK, OLD‐TIMER, DON’T YOU TRY

00:14:06.860 --> 00:14:07.895
TO BE THE VICTIM IN THIS

00:14:07.895 --> 00:14:08.462
SCENARIO.

00:14:08.462 --> 00:14:10.033
&gt;&gt; HEY, HOW DARE YOU?!

00:14:10.033 --> 00:14:10.868
&gt;&gt; DON’T SPEAK TO THE HIGH

00:14:10.868 --> 00:14:11.870
PRIEST LIKE THAT!

00:14:11.870 --> 00:14:13.406
&gt;&gt; Simon: COME ON. LET IT GO.

00:14:13.406 --> 00:14:14.408
IT’S JUST THE WAY IT IS HERE.

00:14:14.408 --> 00:14:15.276
IT’S THE LAW.

00:14:15.276 --> 00:14:16.345
IT’S NOT LIKE THEY’RE THROWING

00:14:16.345 --> 00:14:17.347
THOSE KIDS OUT BECAUSE THEY

00:14:17.347 --> 00:14:17.982
WANT TO.

00:14:17.982 --> 00:14:18.850
&gt;&gt; Kamina: IF YOU REALLY DON’T

00:14:18.850 --> 00:14:19.552
WANT TO DO IT, ALL YOU’VE GOTTA

00:14:19.552 --> 00:14:21.121
DO IS NOT DO IT!

00:14:21.121 --> 00:14:22.123
JUST WHO THE HELL DO YOU THINK

00:14:22.123 --> 00:14:23.159
I AM?!

00:14:23.159 --> 00:14:24.027
I’M KAMINA.

00:14:24.027 --> 00:14:25.296
AND KAMINA WOULD RATHER DIE

00:14:25.296 --> 00:14:26.331
THAN DO SOMETHING HE DOESN’T

00:14:26.331 --> 00:14:27.000
WANNA DO!

00:14:27.000 --> 00:14:28.837
NOW LISTEN UP REAL GOOD!

00:14:28.837 --> 00:14:29.972
THIS HIGH PRIEST OF YOURS IS

00:14:29.972 --> 00:14:30.507
A FRAUD, AND HE’S BEEN

00:14:30.507 --> 00:14:31.408
SPOON‐FEEDING YOU A LOAD OF

00:14:31.408 --> 00:14:32.377
CRAP!

00:14:32.377 --> 00:14:33.446
DON’T FALL FOR IT!

00:14:33.446 --> 00:14:34.281
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: PLEASE STOP THIS

00:14:34.281 --> 00:14:35.216
RIGHT NOW!

00:14:35.216 --> 00:14:36.118
WHAT DO YOU KNOW OF LIFE IN OUR

00:14:36.118 --> 00:14:36.619
VILLAGE?

00:14:36.619 --> 00:14:39.257
WHAT DO YOU KNOW OF HOW WE LIVE?

00:14:39.257 --> 00:14:41.095
&gt;&gt; Kamina: AH! ALL RIGHT,

00:14:41.095 --> 00:14:41.930
FOREHEAD, YOU’RE FINALLY

00:14:41.930 --> 00:14:43.032
STARTING TO SPEAK MY LANGUAGE.

00:14:43.032 --> 00:14:44.535
&gt;&gt; STOP THIS AT ONCE!

00:14:44.535 --> 00:14:46.305
DO NOT RESORT TO VIOLENCE!

00:14:46.305 --> 00:14:47.240
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I DON’T UNDERSTAND

00:14:47.240 --> 00:14:48.510
THIS AT ALL!

00:14:48.510 --> 00:14:50.413
HOW CAN THESE PEOPLE BE

00:14:50.413 --> 00:14:52.383
MESSENGERS SENT FROM THE GODS?

00:14:52.383 --> 00:14:53.486
&gt;&gt; ENDURE THIS.

00:14:53.486 --> 00:14:54.454
THE GODS ARE TESTING OUR FAITH

00:14:54.454 --> 00:14:55.356
AND RESOLVE.

00:14:55.356 --> 00:14:56.158
&gt;&gt; Kamina: COME ON, MAN!

00:14:56.158 --> 00:14:56.893
BRING IT ON!

00:14:56.893 --> 00:14:58.429
&gt;&gt; STOP IT, ROSSIU!

00:14:58.429 --> 00:14:59.397
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THE MIGHTY KAMINA’LL

00:14:59.397 --> 00:15:00.667
TAKE YOU ON!

00:15:00.667 --> 00:15:01.503
YO, FOREHEAD BOY!

00:15:01.503 --> 00:15:03.005
WHAT ARE YOU, A MAN OR A MOUSE?

00:15:03.005 --> 00:15:04.976
MAN OR MOUSE, MAN OR MOUSE,

00:15:04.976 --> 00:15:05.476
MAN OR‐‐?

00:15:05.476 --> 00:15:06.646
[explosion]

00:15:06.646 --> 00:15:08.382
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?!

00:15:08.382 --> 00:15:14.194
[gasps]

00:15:14.194 --> 00:15:17.434
[people yelling]

00:15:17.434 --> 00:15:23.446
&gt;&gt; IT’S ANOTHER FACE GOD!

00:15:23.446 --> 00:15:24.615
&gt;&gt; I HAVE FOUND YOU,

00:15:24.615 --> 00:15:30.493
GURREN LAGANN!

00:15:30.493 --> 00:15:31.462
&gt;&gt; Yoko: SIMON, KAMINA!

00:15:31.462 --> 00:15:34.000
COME ON, GUYS, GET MOVING!

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:35.002
&gt;&gt; Kamina: ALL RIGHT!

00:15:35.002 --> 00:15:36.539
THANKS, YOKO!

00:15:36.539 --> 00:15:37.675
&gt;&gt; STOP THIS!

00:15:37.675 --> 00:15:38.510
WHAT DO YOU THINK YOU’RE DOING

00:15:38.510 --> 00:15:39.444
TO THE FACE GOD?

00:15:39.444 --> 00:15:40.948
&gt;&gt; THE GODS WILL SMITE YOU!

00:15:40.948 --> 00:15:41.683
[sighs]

00:15:41.683 --> 00:15:43.452
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THIS IS GETTING OLD

00:15:43.452 --> 00:15:44.187
REALLY FAST.

00:15:51.101 --> 00:15:52.237
&gt;&gt; Simon: BRO!

00:15:52.237 --> 00:15:53.272
&gt;&gt; Kamina: READY!

00:15:53.272 --> 00:15:56.311
LET’S DO THIS WITH STYLE!

00:16:00.052 --> 00:16:02.558
[grunts]

00:16:16.553 --> 00:16:19.291
[laughs]

00:16:34.589 --> 00:16:38.195
&gt;&gt; Both: BROTHERLY COMBINING!

00:16:38.195 --> 00:16:41.368
GURREN LAGANN!

00:16:52.056 --> 00:16:53.693
&gt;&gt; ONE FACE GOD IS BATTLING

00:16:53.693 --> 00:16:54.729
ANOTHER FACE GOD!

00:16:54.729 --> 00:16:56.566
&gt;&gt; BUT HOW CAN THIS BE?!

00:16:56.566 --> 00:16:57.735
&gt;&gt; Kamina: YOU GUYS DOWN THERE,

00:16:57.735 --> 00:16:58.503
WHAT’RE YOU STANDING

00:16:58.503 --> 00:16:59.170
AROUND FOR?!

00:16:59.170 --> 00:17:00.707
YOU’RE IN THE WAY!

00:17:07.053 --> 00:17:09.357
[yells]

00:17:09.357 --> 00:17:15.469
[Gunmen growls]

00:17:15.469 --> 00:17:16.171
&gt;&gt; Kamina: THESE THINGS

00:17:16.171 --> 00:17:17.073
AREN’T GODS!

00:17:17.073 --> 00:17:18.108
I’M TELLING YOU PEOPLE,

00:17:18.108 --> 00:17:19.612
THESE THINGS ARE THE ENEMY!

00:17:19.612 --> 00:17:20.446
THEY’RE THE ENEMY WE FIGHT

00:17:20.446 --> 00:17:21.549
AGAINST!

00:17:21.549 --> 00:17:22.350
&gt;&gt; Simon: DON’T BOTHER, BRO!

00:17:22.350 --> 00:17:23.185
IT’S NO USE!

00:17:23.185 --> 00:17:24.354
THESE PEOPLE DOWN HERE HAVE

00:17:24.354 --> 00:17:26.058
SPENT THEIR ENTIRE LIVES

00:17:26.058 --> 00:17:27.227
BELIEVING THAT GUNMEN ARE GODS!

00:17:27.227 --> 00:17:30.066
&gt;&gt; Kamina: IN THAT CASE...

00:17:30.066 --> 00:17:31.736
WE’RE GONNA KICK THIS THING’S

00:17:31.736 --> 00:17:34.307
ASS RIGHT IN FRONT OF THEM!

00:17:34.307 --> 00:17:35.476
THAT’LL MAKE ’EM SEE SOME SENSE

00:17:35.476 --> 00:17:37.781
WHETHER THEY WANT TO OR NOT!

00:17:37.781 --> 00:17:39.084
&gt;&gt; Simon: COME ON, BRO!

00:17:39.084 --> 00:17:40.052
I THINK YOU’RE OVERDOING IT!

00:17:40.052 --> 00:17:40.587
&gt;&gt; Kamina: BUTT OUT!

00:17:40.587 --> 00:17:42.090
[thunderous footsteps]

00:17:42.090 --> 00:17:45.396
[yells]

00:17:45.396 --> 00:17:47.166
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHAT THE‐‐?

00:17:47.166 --> 00:17:51.108
&gt;&gt; THE IDOL!

00:17:51.108 --> 00:17:52.443
&gt;&gt; HOW DARE YOU?!

00:17:52.443 --> 00:17:54.649
DON’T INTERFERE, YOU PIECE

00:17:54.649 --> 00:17:55.784
OF JUNK!

00:17:55.784 --> 00:17:58.556
[Gunmen grunting]

00:18:08.442 --> 00:18:10.514
WHAT THE HELL?!

00:18:36.231 --> 00:18:36.866
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: FATHER, WHAT ARE YOU

00:18:36.866 --> 00:18:38.268
DOING IN THERE?

00:18:38.268 --> 00:18:40.641
I WANT AN EXPLANATION.

00:18:45.851 --> 00:18:46.786
[grunts]

00:18:46.786 --> 00:18:49.424
NO! FATHER MAGIN!

00:18:59.477 --> 00:19:00.781
[exhales]

00:19:00.781 --> 00:19:06.325
[scoffs]

00:19:06.325 --> 00:19:07.293
&gt;&gt; Kamina: MAN, I DO NOT LIKE

00:19:07.293 --> 00:19:07.895
YOU.

00:19:07.895 --> 00:19:09.431
I DO NOT LIKE YOU AT ALL,

00:19:09.431 --> 00:19:09.899
OLD‐TIMER.

00:19:09.899 --> 00:19:11.368
IF YOU HAD THAT MUCH SPIRIT,

00:19:11.368 --> 00:19:13.172
WHY DIDN’T YOU‐‐

00:19:13.172 --> 00:19:14.508
&gt;&gt; I SIMPLY MIMICKED WHAT I SAW

00:19:14.508 --> 00:19:15.811
YOU DO, NOTHING MORE.

00:19:15.811 --> 00:19:17.514
I MYSELF DID NOT UNDERSTAND

00:19:17.514 --> 00:19:18.917
THE THINGS I WAS DOING.

00:19:18.917 --> 00:19:20.486
AND NOW I BEG OF YOU TO PLEASE

00:19:20.486 --> 00:19:21.522
LEAVE.

00:19:21.522 --> 00:19:23.593
DO NOT DISTURB OUR VILLAGE

00:19:23.593 --> 00:19:23.927
ANY FURTHER!

00:19:23.927 --> 00:19:25.296
&gt;&gt; Kamina: WHAT DID YOU SAY?

00:19:25.296 --> 00:19:26.465
&gt;&gt; Simon: LET IT GO, BRO!

00:19:26.465 --> 00:19:27.601
IT’S NOT LIKE HE’S SAYING

00:19:27.601 --> 00:19:28.536
ANYTHING WRONG.

00:19:28.536 --> 00:19:29.605
HE’S ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.

00:19:29.605 --> 00:19:30.741
WE DON’T BELONG HERE IN THIS

00:19:30.741 --> 00:19:31.408
VILLAGE.

00:19:31.408 --> 00:19:34.214
WE SHOULD GO.

00:19:34.214 --> 00:19:36.886
&gt;&gt; Kamina: I JUST DON’T GET IT.

00:19:36.886 --> 00:19:39.592
I DON’T GET IT, NOT ONE DAMN

00:19:39.592 --> 00:19:42.397
BIT.

00:19:51.314 --> 00:19:52.785
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: PERHAPS IT’S TIME YOU

00:19:52.785 --> 00:19:54.622
TOLD EVERYONE THE TRUTH.

00:19:54.622 --> 00:19:55.857
&gt;&gt; AND WHAT IS THIS TRUTH I

00:19:55.857 --> 00:19:57.260
WOULD TELL?

00:19:57.260 --> 00:19:58.696
THE KNOWLEDGE WOULD ONLY SERVE

00:19:58.696 --> 00:20:00.499
TO DESTROY OUR VILLAGE.

00:20:00.499 --> 00:20:01.602
DO THEY REALLY NEED TO KNOW

00:20:01.602 --> 00:20:03.205
THE TRUTH?

00:20:03.205 --> 00:20:05.342
WE DO NOT HAVE THE RESOURCES

00:20:05.342 --> 00:20:07.781
TO SUSTAIN A LARGE POPULATION.

00:20:07.781 --> 00:20:08.917
THE FIRST THING I DID WHEN I

00:20:08.917 --> 00:20:10.954
BECAME LEADER OF THE VILLAGE WAS

00:20:10.954 --> 00:20:12.891
TO DECIDE THAT OUR MAXIMUM

00:20:12.891 --> 00:20:16.465
POPULATION MUST BE CAPPED AT 50.

00:20:16.465 --> 00:20:17.601
WE MUST NOT EXCEED THAT NUMBER,

00:20:17.601 --> 00:20:18.903
NOT EVEN BY ONE.

00:20:18.903 --> 00:20:20.540
IF WE SUCCUMB TO SENTIMENTALITY

00:20:20.540 --> 00:20:21.843
OR EMOTION, THEN OUR VILLAGE

00:20:21.843 --> 00:20:23.680
WILL BE LOST.

00:20:23.680 --> 00:20:27.220
FOR ME, THAT IS THE ONLY TRUTH.

00:20:27.220 --> 00:20:28.957
MY RELIGION IS MERELY A TOOL

00:20:28.957 --> 00:20:32.631
I EMPLOY TO ACHIEVE THAT END.

00:20:32.631 --> 00:20:33.833
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: AND WHAT ABOUT GIMMY

00:20:33.833 --> 00:20:35.202
AND DARRY BEING CHOSEN?

00:20:35.202 --> 00:20:36.973
WAS THAT YOUR DOING, FATHER?

00:20:36.973 --> 00:20:38.475
&gt;&gt; YES, BECAUSE THEY ARE

00:20:38.475 --> 00:20:39.812
ORPHANS.

00:20:39.812 --> 00:20:41.281
WITH NO FAMILY, THERE ARE FEW

00:20:41.281 --> 00:20:42.985
LEFT BEHIND WHO WOULD GRIEVE

00:20:42.985 --> 00:20:43.686
FOR THEM.

00:20:43.686 --> 00:20:45.489
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YOU MUST BE JOKING!

00:20:45.489 --> 00:20:46.859
IF THAT’S TRUE, WELL, THEN

00:20:46.859 --> 00:20:51.536
WHAT ABOUT MY MOTHER?!

00:20:51.536 --> 00:20:52.971
&gt;&gt; WHATEVER REGRETS I ONCE HAD,

00:20:52.971 --> 00:20:55.376
I MADE MY PEACE WITH THEM

00:20:55.376 --> 00:20:56.913
LONG AGO.

00:21:00.654 --> 00:21:04.829
[interested chatter]

00:21:04.829 --> 00:21:06.298
&gt;&gt; HERE, TAKE THESE TOO.

00:21:06.298 --> 00:21:08.503
&gt;&gt; BUT WE CAN’T EAT THIS MUCH!

00:21:08.503 --> 00:21:09.905
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE NOT SUPPOSED TO EAT IT

00:21:09.905 --> 00:21:11.007
ALL AT ONCE, CHILD.

00:21:11.007 --> 00:21:12.376
EAT A LITTLE AT A TIME AND

00:21:12.376 --> 00:21:13.312
MAKE IT LAST.

00:21:13.312 --> 00:21:15.349
&gt;&gt; together: OKAY!

00:21:15.349 --> 00:21:17.688
&gt;&gt; ROSSIU, YOU MEAN TO DO THIS?

00:21:17.688 --> 00:21:18.790
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I DO.

00:21:18.790 --> 00:21:19.859
I WILL ACCOMPANY THOSE CHILDREN

00:21:19.859 --> 00:21:21.294
ON THEIR JOURNEY.

00:21:21.294 --> 00:21:22.296
ONCE WE RECLAIM THE SURFACE

00:21:22.296 --> 00:21:25.002
AS A HOME FOR HUMANITY,

00:21:25.002 --> 00:21:26.371
THERE WILL NO LONGER BE ANY

00:21:26.371 --> 00:21:28.008
NEED TO ALLOW OURSELVES TO BE

00:21:28.008 --> 00:21:29.979
BOUND BY SUCH PAINFUL LAWS.

00:21:29.979 --> 00:21:31.616
BESIDES, WON’T IT BE EASIER

00:21:31.616 --> 00:21:32.049
FOR YOU?

00:21:32.049 --> 00:21:33.051
NOBODY ELSE IN THE VILLAGE

00:21:33.051 --> 00:21:34.622
WILL KNOW THE TRUTH.

00:21:34.622 --> 00:21:35.690
NO ONE BUT YOU, SO YOUR

00:21:35.690 --> 00:21:38.830
SECRET’LL BE SAFE.

00:21:38.830 --> 00:21:40.834
&gt;&gt; I UNDERSTAND.

00:21:40.834 --> 00:21:42.838
IN THAT CASE, WOULD YOU LIKE

00:21:42.838 --> 00:21:44.340
TO TAKE THE HOLY SCRIPTURES

00:21:44.340 --> 00:21:45.777
WITH YOU ON YOUR JOURNEY?

00:21:45.777 --> 00:21:47.346
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: THANK YOU, BUT I‐I NO

00:21:47.346 --> 00:21:48.550
LONGER BELIEVE.

00:21:48.550 --> 00:21:49.952
BESIDES, I THOUGHT YOU KNEW

00:21:49.952 --> 00:21:52.056
A CERTAIN SOMETHING ABOUT ME.

00:21:52.056 --> 00:21:53.292
I CAN’T EXACTLY READ,

00:21:53.292 --> 00:21:53.993
FATHER MAGIN.

00:21:53.993 --> 00:21:55.296
&gt;&gt; OH, IS THAT A FACT, MY BOY?

00:21:55.296 --> 00:21:56.933
WELL, YOU NEEDN’T WORRY MUCH

00:21:56.933 --> 00:21:58.302
ABOUT THAT.

00:21:58.302 --> 00:22:00.941
I CAN’T EXACTLY READ, EITHER!

00:22:00.941 --> 00:22:06.786
[gasps]

00:22:06.786 --> 00:22:09.324
WELL, THEN THIS BOOK MAY BE NO

00:22:09.324 --> 00:22:10.560
MORE THAN DEAD WEIGHT TO YOU

00:22:10.560 --> 00:22:12.063
NOW.

00:22:12.063 --> 00:22:13.633
EVEN SO, I WOULD LIKE YOU

00:22:13.633 --> 00:22:14.400
TO TAKE IT WITH YOU ON YOUR

00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:16.672
JOURNEY.

00:22:16.672 --> 00:22:20.914
PLEASE ACCEPT IT.

00:22:20.914 --> 00:22:22.985
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YES, FATHER.

