&gt;&gt; Kamina: IF IT’S INVISIBLE,

00:24:19.484 --> 00:24:19.985
YOU WANT TO SEE IT!

00:24:19.985 --> 00:24:20.854
IF YOU’RE TOLD NOT TO LOOK,

00:24:20.854 --> 00:24:21.889
YOU CAN’T RESIST PEEKING!

00:24:21.889 --> 00:24:23.593
IF IT’S HIDDEN, YOU WANNA

00:24:23.593 --> 00:24:23.926
FIND IT!

00:24:23.926 --> 00:24:25.162
THAT’S WHAT A MAN’S ADVENTURE

00:24:25.162 --> 00:24:26.164
IS ALL ABOUT!

